    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>05 March 1953</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 512</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-957b0c17-4f32-4d99-90b5-a562e4b33644'>
            
<p class="">45.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f">
                Mr. Simmons
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-03-05/debates/10b9d91d-c07a-4eb3-8fa1-002818e1fdc0/Amalgamation#contribution-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister if he will consider publication of the White Paper on the extinction of the Ministry of Pensions at a date <span id="543" class="column-number" data-column-number="543"></span> considerably earlier than the end of April in order to allow ex-Service organisations adequate time to consider its contents, and possible representations, before irrevocable steps have been taken.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-03-05/debates/10b9d91d-c07a-4eb3-8fa1-002818e1fdc0/Amalgamation#contribution-7d0de4d3-639d-494a-9d5b-2cf0298dd99f">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-03-05/debates/10b9d91d-c07a-4eb3-8fa1-002818e1fdc0/Amalgamation#contribution-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It will not be possible to present the White Paper before the end of April. But as it is not intended that the amalgamation between the Ministries of Pensions and National Insurance will take place before 1st August at the earliest, ample time will be available for the making of representations by people wishing to do so.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-03-05/debates/10b9d91d-c07a-4eb3-8fa1-002818e1fdc0/Amalgamation#contribution-c36b5609-6ffa-426d-b192-3bfee0584e8b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028">
                Mr. Simmons
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-03-05/debates/10b9d91d-c07a-4eb3-8fa1-002818e1fdc0/Amalgamation#contribution-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the Prime Minister aware of the necessity for allowing the people most concerned an opportunity of expressing their opinions? Is he aware of the conferences of the ex-Service organisations at Whitsuntide and Easter and also the earlier conferences? They really ought to have the information before they can come to a reasoned and informed decision on the matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-03-05/debates/10b9d91d-c07a-4eb3-8fa1-002818e1fdc0/Amalgamation#contribution-af4703ad-9432-47a7-9ca2-7a2c8f665028">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-b1e31138-980a-4e12-8430-188ddf5ab926">
